2810B8F0.Line7.7FA05: (sigh) Of all people, I never would have expected her to embrace Lilith.

5A334C6A.Line1.7FA05: Yes, Yorin told me. He was just here.

5B80055C.Line21.7FA05: Good. Astaroth’s essence is nearby, but it is contained. Secure. Beyond Lilith’s reach. Speak of this to no one. The last thing we need now is to cause panic.

65381056.Line13.BAE4: There’s more. Before she passed, Airidah spoke of a song that breaks the wards around Astaroth’s chamber. What did she mean? What chamber?

A327237F.Line15.7FA05: Keep your voice down. Does Yorin know?

ABB63129.VoiceDir21.7FA05: Relieved for the first sentence. A bit flustered, gathering himself and trying to be reassuring for the rest of the line.
